    rating: "Pretty Bad"
    comments: "The concept is a standard sequel; the plot structure is pretty simple for the most part, but the final 40 minutes of the movie are completely useless as they start a new storyline; the character writing is good for Pushpa as they continue to build this memorable character for this character driven franchise"
  }
