    comments: "A lot of grand sets, and helps make this movie feel very South Indian"
  }
  pacing: "Pacing is very slow as it feels like they are dragging the story out"
  climax: "Climax is unnecessary as they added a brand new storyline that added nothing to the original storyline; this could have been cut and the movie could have been a lot tighter"
  tone: "Tone is very action-Tollywood"
  final_notes: ""
  overall: "Overall, a Tollywood sequel with traditional South Indian action sequences and a memorable character performance from Allu Arjun, but the bloated story makes this movie run for a lot longer than it needs to"
